    public abstract class TemplateRoutineBuilder<INPUT,OUTPUT>
extends TemplateRoutine<INPUT,OUTPUT>
implements RoutineBuilder<INPUT,OUTPUT>
    Empty abstract implementation of a routine builder.

    This class is useful to avoid the need of implementing some of the methods defined in the interface. Created by davide on 3/16/15.
